data.description: Explore the serenity of this spacious 3-bedroom, 3-bath home on 3.64 private acres, providing 1,248 sq ft on the main level. With a 2-car detached garage and a full basement that's partially finished, this property offers room for your vision. Embrace the seclusion and natural beauty of the surroundings, with easy access to numerous lakes and a connection to the Chippewa National Forest. Remer is known for its tranquil living, providing a retreat from the hustle and bustle while offering a gateway to outdoor adventures. This property presents an opportunity to create your ideal up-north haven
